🧩 Folder Structure
📦 maritime-weather-dashboard
├── app.py                    # Streamlit dashboard
├── maritime_weather_ui.py    # Flask web UI
├── weather_updater.py        # API-based weather fetcher
├── final.csv                 # Master port data
├── weather_by_country/       # Folder for generated CSVs
└── README.md

